<i>Posted by Dikamek Skunkbane on 03-17-2004 07:06 AM:</i>

<p><b> 5th Year EverQuest Anniversary Promotions</b></p>

<p><a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/anniversary_promotions.jsp" target="_blank">http://eqlive.station.sony.com/anni..._promotions.jsp</a><br />
<br />
<img src="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/images/featured/small/feature_5th_savings.jpg" border="0" alt=""> <br />
<br />
<blockquote><font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1">quote:</font><hr><img src="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/images/5thAnnPromoTop.jpg" border="0" alt=""><br />
Sign up now for a one year subscription of SOE All Access and save over $63! For two weeks only, we are offering a special 5th Anniversary one-year subscription for SOE All Access, the premier gaming pass that lets you play 7 great games for one very low price. Sign up between March 16, 2004 and March 30, 2004 to take advantage of  fantastic savings! <br />
<br />
This is a one time deal for a 12-month subscription and an opportunity for great savings. At the end of the subscription year, your SOE All Access account will roll over to the then current monthly recurring subscription (currently $21.99 per month). <br />
<br />
New York State and Texas residents will be charged sales tax. Additionally, residents of VAT-applicable European Union territories will also be charged a VAT equal to 17.5% of the applicable fee.<br />
<br />
The subscription charges are in addition to the cost of each games*. You will need to purchase a copy of each of the games from a retail store or online at the Station Store. The price of the games will vary depending upon the store. <br />
<br />
*The Station Pass games, Infantry, Tanarus and Cosmic Rift are available for free download.<hr></blockquote><br />
<br />
<blockquote><font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1">quote:</font><hr><img src="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/images/5thAnnPromoText.gif" border="0" alt=""><br />
Sign up for a one year subscription between March 16, 2004 and March 30, 2004 and you'll lock in great savings on your EverQuest subscription. Your new, lower cost, annual subscription will take effect at the end of your current billing cycle, saving you money and extending your adventures for an entire year. <br />
<br />
That's not all! Since an EverQuest subscription is recurring, you'll only pay $99.99 for your second year, and so on, for continued savings! <br />
<br />
Don't wait! This special opportunity will not last long. <br />
<br />
New York State and Texas residents will be charged sales tax. Additionally, residents of VAT-applicable European Union territories will also be charged a VAT equal to 17.5% of the applicable fee. <br />
<br />
Please note: The subscription charges are in addition to the cost of the game. You will need to purchase a copy of the game from a retail store or online at the Station Store. The price of the game will vary depending upon the store.<hr></blockquote><!-- BEGIN TEMPLATE: postbit_signature -->
